snippet.title: Tekken 7 – E3 Trailer | XB1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
TEKKEN 7 has been confirmed for the Xbox One, PC, and PlayStation 4! See a snapshot between the infamous Heihachi and raging Akuma. The game is launching in Early 2017 so get hyped and share this trailer with all your friends. 

Follow TEKKEN on all these platforms to keep up to date with all the new TEKKEN News!
